nodes.text: The Mos Eisley Parade was an event held in Mos Eisley, Tatooine by the Hutts to crown the Miss Mos Eisley. It featured the Max Rebo Band and Figrin D'an and the Modal Nodes and saw Imperial presence.
This event appears in the online game Star Wars Galactic Spy, which includes a number of Prequel era characters and elements dispersed among the largely Imperial era setting.
